To meet the requirement of secure user sessions that expire after 15 minutes of inactivity, we need to configure our Flask application to manage session expiration. We'll be relying on Flask extensions for JWT to manage token-based sessions. We will set the `JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRES` configuration to 15 minutes and ensure that tokens are refreshed to maintain session validity while users are active.

Epic Title: User Authentication and Security

We will utilize the existing project structure and add necessary configurations and routes to handle session management.

